#Cleric
Monk:

NOTES: Potentially change DODGE into the skill that makes someone spend a maneuver to prepare for ranged/melee attack. Potentially have two types and have them thematically switch to different forms - Attack/Defense. Character then essentially makes prep choices at beginning of combat re: how they will fight. Abilities make it easier to switch forms mid-combat. 

