#Abilities
A1/A2/A3/A4 - Replaced with Body, Mind and Spirit As One with wording as “A monk seeks balance and harmony both within and without - enabling him to exceed physical and mental limits.  Once per encounter as a maneuver the character may roll a Spirit check to upgrade his next skill check. For an Easy Check (D), Spend 2 strain to Upgrade Once; For an Average (DD) Check, Spend 4 strain to Upgrade twice; Hard Check, Spend 6 strain to Upgrade three times. Upgrades do not stack.  If the character fails to succeed on the check they must upgrade the difficulty of the next check once.” Cost 10 Link to B1,B2 and B3/B4
B1 - Replaced with Purest Form wording as “When performing the As One maneuver, the character may spend 2 ADVANTAGE to apply As One upgrades to 1 additional skill check per encounter.” Cost 10 link to B2 and C1
B2 - Replaced  with Years of Training wording as “Spend 3 Strain as an incidental to gain soak equal ranks in Resilience for one round””When attacked spend 3 strain to double all soak not gained from armour, for that attack” Cost 10 link to B1 and C2/C3
B3/B4 - Replaced with Spirit Blast wording as “By spending 3 strain the character may perform the Spirit Blast action at an enemy at Short Range.  Make an average Spirit check, if successful dealing 7 damage plus 1 per SUCCESS, with Blast 6” Clost 10 link to C2/C3 and C4
C1 - Replaced with Soft Form wording as “After a successful unarmed melee check to inflict strain damage, the character may spend ADVANTAGE to disarm the opponent.  If disarmed a TRIUMPH may be spent to gain control of the weapon.” cost 5 link to C2/C3 and D1
C2/C3 - Replaced with Flaming Uppercut wording as “The character as an attack action may spend 3 strain to make an unarmed melee check against an opponent at Engaged range.  If successful deal damage equal to Brawn+6 and Disorient 2.  May spend TRIUMPH to stagger the target for 1 round for each TRIUMPH spent.” Cost 15 link to C1, D2 and D3
C4 - Replaced with Longest Breath wording as “The character may spend up to 2 strain to increase the range of Spirit Blast by one range band equal to the strain spent: Cost 10 Link to D4


